<div style="margin-left: 5%;margin-right: 5%;">
    <div class="row">
        <a href="/products/viewLowQuantityProducts" style="color: white ">
            <div class="well col-sm-4" style="background-color:#6c6a79; height: 200px; ">
                <h2>Low in Stock {{quantity}}<span class="pull-right"><img
                            src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/000000/low-battery.png"></span></h2>
                            <p>Shows the products that are low in stock, i.e. less than 5. It would also notify in the notification bar. Immediately place an order with the supplier of the products which are low in stock.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/orders/newOrders" style="color: white ">
            <div class="well col-sm-4" style="background-color: #63768d; height: 200px;  ">
                <h2>
                    New Orders {{new_order}}
                    <span class="pull-right">
                        <img src="https://img.icons8.com/bubbles/48/000000/violet-shopping-basket.png"></span>
                </h2>
                <p>Shows the number of newly placed orders by the customer. A notification will pop-up in the notification bar. Proceed the orders immediately after receiving.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/forum/viewNewPost" style="color: white ">
            <div class="well col-sm-4" style="background-color: #3c709a; height: 200px;  ">
                <h2>New Posts {{newPost}}<span class="pull-right"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/office/48/000000/chat.png"></span></h2>
            <p>Shows the number of new posts in the Forum. A notification in the notification bar will alert about new posts. Approve or block posts soon after it is made.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>